[30;1m285 | [0m[35mis simple, cheap and fast, but CodeBuild cannot guarantee a reuse of instance[0m
[30;1m286 | [0m[35mand hence cannot guarantee cache hits. For example, when a build starts and[0m
[30;1m287 | [0m[35mcaches files locally, if two subsequent builds start at the same time afterwards[0m

[30;1m289 | [0m[35msupported, which can be turned on individually.[0m
